{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"00fdb8e252ec8a7396bf8e","title":"2026-05-15 首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367058,"created":1780371330025,"custom":{},"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-15_首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"383cdef34ffb3085a5da4690b917ae23","links":[],"anchors":{"2026-05-15-首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"2026-05-15 首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录","value":"2026-05-15-首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"需求背景":{"type":"header","text":"需求背景","value":"需求背景","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"涉及文件":{"type":"header","text":"涉及文件","value":"涉及文件","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"变更内容":{"type":"header","text":"变更内容","value":"变更内容","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2},"新增隐藏模式掩码宏":{"type":"header","text":"新增隐藏模式掩码宏","value":"新增隐藏模式掩码宏","line":20,"column":0,"depth":3},"新增辅助函数":{"type":"header","text":"新增辅助函数","value":"新增辅助函数","line":44,"column":0,"depth":3},"修改模式切换逻辑":{"type":"header","text":"修改模式切换逻辑","value":"修改模式切换逻辑","line":61,"column":0,"depth":3},"修改初始化逻辑":{"type":"header","text":"修改初始化逻辑","value":"修改初始化逻辑","line":72,"column":0,"depth":3},"恢复方法":{"type":"header","text":"恢复方法","value":"恢复方法","line":81,"column":0,"depth":2},"方法一改代码推荐":{"type":"header","text":"方法一：改代码（推荐）","value":"方法一改代码推荐","line":83,"column":0,"depth":3},"方法二编译时覆盖":{"type":"header","text":"方法二：编译时覆盖","value":"方法二编译时覆盖","line":90,"column":0,"depth":3},"影响范围":{"type":"header","text":"影响范围","value":"影响范围","line":96,"column":0,"depth":2},"编译验证":{"type":"header","text":"编译验证","value":"编译验证","line":103,"column":0,"depth":2},"备注":{"type":"header","text":"备注","value":"备注","line":110,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"jxzspjsfkjpyzxdrn5ntdy7","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"2026-05-15-首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录\">2026-05-15 首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-15-首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"2026-05-15-首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录-1\">2026-05-15 首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-15-首页六模式隐藏功能开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"需求背景\">需求背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#需求背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>首页六个打印模式（动漫、卡通、水墨画、线条画、简笔画、速写）中，动漫、水墨画、简笔画三个模式打印效果不佳，需要暂时从首页轮播中隐藏。但代码不能删除，后续打印效果改善后需要恢复显示。</p>\n<h2 id=\"涉及文件\">涉及文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#涉及文件\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.c</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"变更内容\">变更内容<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#变更内容\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"新增隐藏模式掩码宏\">新增隐藏模式掩码宏<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#新增隐藏模式掩码宏\"></a></h3>\n<p>在 <code>UI_STATUS_TIME_PLACEHOLDER</code> 定义之后、<code>ui_mode_next_visible</code> 函数之前，新增：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">/*\n * Bitmask of mode indices hidden from desktop rotation.\n * Bit 0=anime, 1=cartoon, 2=ink_wash, 3=line_art, 4=simple_drawing, 5=sketch.\n * Set to 0 to show all six modes; set (1&#x3C;&#x3C;0)|(1&#x3C;&#x3C;2)|(1&#x3C;&#x3C;4) to hide anime/ink/simple.\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">ifndef</span> <span class=\"token expression\">LV_DESKTOP_HIDDEN_MODE_MASK</span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">LV_DESKTOP_HIDDEN_MODE_MASK</span> <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1U</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1U</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1U</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">endif</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>隐藏的模式</strong>：\n| 位 | 索引 | 模式名 | 枚举键 |\n|----|------|--------|--------|\n| 0  | 0    | 动漫   | anime  |\n| 2  | 2    | 水墨画 | ink_wash |\n| 4  | 4    | 简笔画 | simple_drawing |</p>\n<p><strong>保留的模式</strong>：卡通(1)、线条画/线稿(3)、速写/素描(5)</p>\n<h3 id=\"新增辅助函数\">新增辅助函数<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#新增辅助函数\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span> <span class=\"token function\">ui_mode_next_visible</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span> cur<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> MODE_SLOT_COUNT<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        cur <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>cur <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> MODE_SLOT_COUNT<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>LV_DESKTOP_HIDDEN_MODE_MASK <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1U</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;&#x3C;</span> cur<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> cur<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> cur<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>从当前索引出发，循环查找下一个未被掩码标记的可见模式。</p>\n<h3 id=\"修改模式切换逻辑\">修改模式切换逻辑<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#修改模式切换逻辑\"></a></h3>\n<p><code>desktop_next_cb()</code> 中：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 旧代码</span>\ns_mode_idx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_mode_idx <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token function\">ui_mode_count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 新代码</span>\ns_mode_idx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">ui_mode_next_visible</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_mode_idx<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"修改初始化逻辑\">修改初始化逻辑<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#修改初始化逻辑\"></a></h3>\n<p><code>lv_example_meter()</code> 中，如果初始索引 0 在隐藏列表中，则自动跳到第一个可见模式：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\">s_mode_idx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>LV_DESKTOP_HIDDEN_MODE_MASK <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1U</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;&#x3C;</span> s_mode_idx<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    s_mode_idx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">ui_mode_next_visible</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_mode_idx<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"恢复方法\">恢复方法<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#恢复方法\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"方法一改代码推荐\">方法一：改代码（推荐）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#方法一改代码推荐\"></a></h3>\n<p>将 <code>lv_example_meter.c</code> 中的掩码改为 <code>0</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">LV_DESKTOP_HIDDEN_MODE_MASK</span> <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">0</span></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"方法二编译时覆盖\">方法二：编译时覆盖<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#方法二编译时覆盖\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">scons --beken<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>bk7252n -j4 <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">CCFLAGS</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"-DLV_DESKTOP_HIDDEN_MODE_MASK=0\"</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"影响范围\">影响范围<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#影响范围\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>仅影响首页模式轮播 UI</strong>：用户按键切换模式时跳过隐藏模式</li>\n<li><strong>不影响打印机驱动</strong>：<code>thermal_printer.c</code> 通过模式名字符串匹配参数，不受掩码影响</li>\n<li><strong>不影响多语言字符串</strong>：<code>ui_strings.c</code> 中的模式名称翻译全部保留</li>\n<li><strong>不影响图标资源</strong>：<code>mode_icons_bmp.c</code> 中的六个图标全部保留</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"编译验证\">编译验证<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#编译验证\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">scons --beken<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>bk7252n -j4\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 编译通过，无错误无警告</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"备注\">备注<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#备注\"></a></h2>\n<p>此方案采用掩码位图方式控制隐藏，扩展性好：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如需隐藏其他模式，只需设置对应位</li>\n<li>支持非连续性隐藏（当前隐藏 0、2、4）</li>\n<li>不影响代码中其他任何对模式索引/名称的引用</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI ��ӡ���̼��ĵ���","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"01a79b7e7f0264a5734e0abe50acd9de","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":96},"end":{"line":8,"column":28,"offset":121},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"�